long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Internal chrome extension for Terrapin Works employees at the University of Maryland. This extension allows one-click printing of labels for print jobs. Just navigate to a job page in the Innovation Center platform, click the extension icon to popup the page shown in the screenshot, an click the button to print.
